{
  "stem": "521.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But, of course, this Jew may have been in a camp for about two, three years, and that's the way he wanted to survive.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But it was still not right because about 15 or 20 of us didn't have anything to eat on that night.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the following day when we went, we went 15 of us, because we were prepared that maybe somebody is going to do the same trick.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, this comes back, here I'm talking against Jews because Jews were coming, and they were pulling the blankets off the people who were sleeping.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And once you didn't have any blanket, you are going to die because it was in April, and April was still cold.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that's why I told you I had even the boot inside of my sleeping bag.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, it came to the point where I didn't have my boot, which I was steal from Hungary.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't good enough anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my only choice was to get one, and the other one, I was taking a boot off a dead man.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I just have taken it off, and I put it on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "These were the ones which were issued by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a wooden sole and a canvas top, that one fitted everybody.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So from then on-- it was very close to the end of the war, and I knew that it's not going to be any more fashion show.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I just-- he was the--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had the Hungarian uniform to the bitter end, until the Americans burned it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It didn't save me any more because we were in the concentration camp, and that was just nothing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had the proper wooden shoe, and we were walking.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
